skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: super charged
Developer Terms of Use
des:
Subscribing to this skill allows you to use the voice service for the following actions:
1. Query the power of the device
2. Turn on/off the ambient light
3. Adjust the color and brightness of the ambient light
4. Query/enable/disable automatic power saving plan, etc.
